title.narrative: ECFIAT - Eastern Caribbean Financial Investigations Advisory Team

description.narrative: This activity (ECFIAT - Eastern Caribbean Financial Investigations Advisory Team) is a component of Eastern Caribbean Financial Investigations Advisory Team (ECFIAT) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Other bilateral donor' and a budget of £1,193,383. This component benefits West Indies, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Anti-corruption organisations and institutions, Security system management and reform. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-04-2010 and the end date is 30-09-2012.
